casebody.data:
No. 3,

Misc.

Scalf v. Skeen, Warden. Petitioner pro se. John G. Fox, Attorney General of West Virginia, and T. D. Kauffelt, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Appeals of West Virginia denied for the reason that the judgment below is based upon a non-federal ground adequate to support it.
